          "blocks": {
            "accordion_row_mM8riD": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What types of ingredients are used in the Cala Falcó Collection?",
                "open_by_default": true,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 200
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_eCzNhx": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>The Cala Falcó Collection is crafted using premium natural ingredients, such as essential oils, botanical extracts, and Mediterranean herbs. You’ll find ingredients like lavender, rosemary, almond oil, and citrus fruits, all selected for their mood-enhancing and skin-nourishing properties​.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
